author: @janvanholthe270
content: The show was paid for by one of Brazil's biggest bank (Itau)+ a beer brand + Globo TV + US$ 2 million dollars from the city of Rio. On the other hand, the revenues generated by the show were more than enough to compensate public cost. It was a wonderful show!
